OL,6,FThe Government is to unveil measures to
OL,7,Fboost growth in UK financial services
OL,8,Fand the City of London.The reforms,
OL,9,Fdubbed "Big Bang 2.0", are aimed at
OL,10,Fbolstering London's post-Brexit
OL,11,Fcompetitiveness and will be revealed by
OL,12,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt.
OL,14,FMoves are expected to include
OL,15,Fconfirmation of the removal of a cap on
OL,16,Fbankers bonuses. Ring-fencing rules
OL,17,Fthat require banks to protect their
OL,18,Fretail banking services from their
OL,19,Friskier investment and international
OL,20,Fbanking activities are also to be
OL,21,Frelaxed.
OL,3,CGovernment reveals 'Big Bang 2.0' deal
OL,4,Cto boost finance after Brexit
